CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1958 , pg. 1 reads: "After Three of Seven Wrecks - These automobiles were among those damaged in seven crashes last week and this week. The wrecks in which these cars were involved occurred in East Liberty, Homewood and the Hill District. Five persons landed in the hospital, when the vehicle, left, ran out of control and his a utility pole in East Liberty..."
TitMainTitle: Chevrolet Deluxe car with passenger side damage parked in salvage lot near mill
